@startuml
title pyArchimate Context Diagram

"pyArchimate" as Library
actor "Designer" as Designer
actor "Automation / Integrations" as Automation
cloud "Archi/Archimate/ARIS sources" as Inputs
rectangle "Archimate XML / Archi models / CSV" as Outputs
rectangle "Readers / Writers" as IO
rectangle "Core Model Builder" as Core
rectangle "Logging subsystem" as Logging

Designer --> Core : create models, add elements, draw views
Automation --> Core : invoke automation scripts or CI jobs
Core --> IO : delegate serialization & deserialization
IO --> Inputs : parse Archi/Archimate/ARIS sources
IO --> Outputs : write Archimate / Archi / CSV exports
Core --> Logging : emit warnings & diagnostics
Core ..> Library : exposes API for scripts, CLIs
Library ..> Inputs : references validation metadata
@enduml
